KIPInfrastructure

The official URL for this implementation guide is: 

https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/ImplementationGuide/dk.kip.rkkp.fhir.ig.core

The Danish Sundhedsvæsenets Kvalitetsinstitut defines a set of FHIR CodeSystems and ValueSets used for data collection.
